---
import { FREEPHONE_NUMBER } from '../../../../../utils/constants';

interface Props {
	location: string;
	locationTel: string;
}

const { location, locationTel } = Astro.props;
---

<h2 class="h3">
	Do you need a Boiler Repair or Service and live in {location} or the surrounding area?
</h2>
<h3 class="h4 coloured-text">
	Call us now on {
		locationTel ? locationTel : `Freephone ${FREEPHONE_NUMBER} - 24 hour Emergency Helpline`
	}
</h3>

<h3 class="h4">
	24-hour Emergency Heating Engineers in {location}
</h3>
<p>
	We understand that the disruption and inconvenience associated with heating problems means that a <strong
		>fast, effective response</strong
	> is needed.
</p>
<p>
	The dedication of our 24-hour emergency heating engineers covering {location}
	means that we aim to be with you <strong>within 2 hours of your call</strong>. What's more, we
	will keep you informed throughout every step of the repair process.
</p>
<h3 class="h4 coloured-text">Boiler breakdown? Choose us for boiler repairs</h3>
<p>
	A boiler breakdown can be expensive, so regular maintenance is essential to ensure its long-term
	performance. Our local team of engineers covering {location} have experience working with Worcester
	Bosch boilers and gas, combi and condensing boilers from many other manufacturers.
</p>
<p>
	Beyond issues with central heating and boilers, we also offer <strong
		>gas safety inspections</strong
	>, <strong>Landlord CP12 certificates</strong> and <strong>homeowner certificates</strong>.
</p>
